    SRM proteomics data from human CSF

    msnset.Rd

    Targeted selected reaction monitoring (SRM) analysis of proteins in human cerebrospinal fluid.

    data(srm_msnset)

    Format

    An MSnSet with 42 features and 42 samples.

    Source

    Add source.

    phenoData

    A data frame consisting of 42 rows (samples) and 82 columns:

    sample.id

    A unique sample identifier. The match group and subject type.

    SampleNum

    A unique sample identifier. Same as Prep Alias.

    match.group

    Strings "01", "02", "04", "05", ..., "19".

    subject.type

    Either "case", "control.1", or "control.2".

    projid

    A unique sample identifier.

    age_death

    Age at death.

    msex

    Sex of the subject. Male is denoted by 1, female by 0.

    race

    The race of the subject. All entries are "White".

    spanish

    All entries are "Not Hispanic".

    educ
    pmi

    An estimate of the time since death (postmortem interval).

    parksc_lv
    dxpark
    cog_reduced
    dlbdx
    henl_4gp
    niareagansc
    amelidrg_ever
    lb_dens_lc:lb_dens
    lb_dens_sn_state

    Non-missing entries are "zero" or "high".

    tang_dens_sn
    tang_dens_sn_state

    Non-missing entries are "zero", "low", or "mid".

    amy_mean_sn
    amy_mean_sn_state

    All non-missing entries are "low".

    dlbany
    dlb_acc
    dlb_ag
    dlb_ec
    dlb_mfc
    dlb_mtc
    dlb_sn
    acaccb12
    acing12
    ah12
    aitb12
    amfc12
    amyag
    amyec
    asf12
    tauag
    tauec
    tcaccb12
    tcing12
    th12
    titb12
    tmfc12
    tsf12
    amy_mean_sn.predicted
    amy_mean_sn.imputed
    amy_mean_state.predicted

    All non-missing entries are "low".

    amy_mean_state.imputed

    All entries are "low".

    tang_dens_sn.predicted
    tang_dens_sn.imputed
    tang_dens_sn_state.predicted

    One of "zero", "low", "mid" or "high".

    tang_dens_sn_state.imputed

    One of "zero", "low", "mid" or "high".

    lb_dens_sn.predicted
    lb_dens_sn.imputed
    lb_dens_sn_state.predicted

    Either "zero" or "high".

    lb_dens_sn_state.imputed

    Either "zero" or "high".

    inclusion

    All entries are TRUE.

    case

    TRUE if subject.type is "case".

    control

    TRUE if subject.type is "control.1" or "control.2".

    match.1
    match.2
    slp_resid
    Prep order

    Integers 1-3.

    Prep Alias

    A unique sample identifier. Same as SampleNum.

    PrepBatch

    Batch number within Prep order. Integers 1-3.

    Coomassie (pre-digest)
    Visible blood contamination

    "contaminated" or blank ("").

    SPE Batch

    Integers 1-4.

    BCA (post-digest)

    The BCA Protein Assay concentration in mg/mL? Used for total protein quantitation.

    Yield (ug)
    Visible blood contamination after SPE

    "contaminated" or blank ("").

    Dilution Volume (Volume Remaing)
    dataset name

    The dataset name. The format is "Levy_CSF_SRM_XX", where "XX" is the Prep Alias.

    Examples

    data("srm_msnset")
